Package: infographiq
Title: Create interactive infographics for data-driven storytelling
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Ben", "Best", email = "ben@ecoquants.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: "Given a scalable vector graphic (*.svg) illustration, link elements (with click and hover) to a modal window (similar to a popup without, but without web browser restriction) that lists plotted objects. These plots could be any plot output (ggplot2, leaflet, dygraphs, etc.). This R package is being developed for the Marine Biodiversity Observation Network project."
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
License: MIT License
Encoding: UTF-8
